movies.title: Alive or Dead
movies.plot: On a desolate road, an abandoned school bus with the words 'HELP ME' written on a window, Maria stops to check it out. A killer has left his bloody crime scene in the back. The killer comes back and takes Maria for a ride to a desert location. But is the killer really her enemy or is it someone, or something else?

biography.bio: Masao Kitamura was born and raised in Oxnard, California. He landed his first acting role as Flotsam in his fourth grade theater production of The Little Mermaid. In 1999, Masao began studying improvisation with Efren Ramirez who later became Pedro in the hit comedy Napoleon Dynamite (2004). In 2006, Masao made his television debut as a zombie for the Spike TV Scream Awards 2006 (2006). Later in 2006, Masao also landed a featured role in Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End (2007) as one of the Asian pirates fighting under Captain Sao Feng, played by Yun-Fat Chow. Masao currently continues his theatrical and improvisational training at L.A. Connection Comedy under Kent Skov.
biography.name: Masao Kitamura

biography.bio: Thomas Crnkovich was an actor, known for Sgt. Kabukiman N.Y.P.D. (1990), The Little Samaritan (2009) and Tales from the Grave, Volume 2: Happy Holidays (2005). He died on May 24, 2013 in Indiana, USA.
biography.name: Thomas Crnkovich
